{"word":"H7201 - רָאָה - râʼâh - raw-aw' - Glede","slug":"H7201","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָאָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râʼâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Glede"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05D0;&#x05D4; - ra&#x0302;'a&#x0302;h</b> - <i>raw-aw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7200\">H7200</a>; a <i>bird</i> of prey (probably the <i>vulture</i>, from its sharp <i>sight</i>): - glede. Compare <a href=\"#/H1676\">H1676</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1675\">H1675</a>, <a href=\"#/H1676\">H1676</a>, <a href=\"#/H1772\">H1772</a>"}]}